<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Our Platform</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: auto;
        }
        .password {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Welcome to Our Platform</h2>
        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        <p>An account has been created for you by the administrator. Here are your login details:</p>
        <p><strong>Username:</strong> {{email}}</p>
        <p class="password"><strong>Password:</strong> {{password}}</p>
        <p>Please log in and change your password for security reasons.</p>
        <div class="footer">&copy; {{year}} {{appname}}. All rights reserved.</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>